# Repo boundaries (proof-library)

This repo is the **published proof corpus dashboard** — catalog vs Lean scan, divergence, human votes.

## Owns

- `web/` Next.js static site (deployed at https://proofs.lilangverse.xyz/)
- `data/library.json`, `data/posture.json` (generated snapshots for Pages)
- `scripts/build-library.py`, `build-posture.py`, `rebuild.sh`

## Never add here

- `proof-db/` specimens, Lean bridge, TOML entries → **lic**
- Benchmark perf matrix, `summary.json`, tier CSV ingest → **benchmarks**
- Compiler or semantics changes → **lic**

## Ingest policy

- Default `LIC_ROOT=../lic` (canonical). Feature-branch worktrees are read-only inputs, not a second home for proof-db.
- Rebuild JSON from lic at CI/Pages time when possible; committed snapshots are fallback for offline builds.

## Cross-repo

- Benchmarks links here; do not copy UI back into benchmarks.
